Aphrodite:

Good to hear your voice--well, you know what I mean. Your attack (ah, it takes
me back to hear you shrieking like that again--back to when this list was
really prime time) happened to include a quotation of my email, as quoted by
someone else. I hope, then, that my breakdown wasn't wrongfully associated
with the attitude you were attacking.

