that scored me a nice hardback for $20) is to search www.mxbf.com every few
weeks or so. This is a search engine that simultaneously checks Amazon, and
five or six other used bookstore posting sites from around the world. There
are literally thousands of new and used bookstores all over the world posting
books of all kinds on these sites and MX Bookfinder searches them all
simultaneously.

I checked a minute ago and there was nothing listed--but it will turn up. It
took a couple of months for me to find it.

Seamus

